    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 mb-12 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute -right-10 -top-10 w-40 h-40 bg-blue-100 rounded-full opacity-50"></div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-blue-900 mb-4 relative z-10">¬øPor qu√© digitalizar tu empresa en 2026?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-blue-800 mb-8 leading-relaxed relative z-10">
          Con la entrada en vigor de la <strong class="text-blue-900 bg-white px-1 rounded shadow-sm">Ley Verifactu</strong>, los aut√≥nomos que sigan usando papel o Excel tendr√°n problemas legales. Elige un software certificado para evitar multas de Hacienda.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 relative z-10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-blue-100">
            <span class="text-2xl">‚úÖ</span>
            <div class="leading-tight">
                <span class="block text-xs text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase">Hacienda</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">Certificado QR</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-blue-100">
            <span class="text-2xl">üì±</span>
            <div class="leading-tight">
                <span class="block text-xs text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase">Movilidad</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">App de Trabajo</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-blue-100">
            <span class="text-2xl">‚òÅÔ∏è</span>
            <div class="leading-tight">
                <span class="block text-xs text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase">Accesible</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">Todo en Nube</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      {/* ICONOS DE CONFIANZA */}
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
        <div>
